                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A mithral golem is not healed by a @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Slow]{Slow} spell, and such spells affect them normally. A @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Haste]{Haste} spell reverses the effects of a <em>slow</em> spell immediately.</p>"
